Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 13: Memories to Come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:52.11,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shisogapo, Lumpur\NInternational Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the purpose of your visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, I need to find someone\Nwith an ability to search.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I'll ask their leader.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:30.86,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A city in the Philippines
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's got to be this one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now... What kind of an ability will he have...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you move, I'll burn everything including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the leader, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An ability-wielder, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why can't I read his mind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... "Why can't I read..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He stole my ability?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This really is a useful ability...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Question: How do you look for ability-wielders?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think... Don't think... Don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that guy's sis is finding the ability-wielders\Nfor you, huh? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Door, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Angelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your ability is an sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to use it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You just have to look at the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His ability to seek ability-wielders is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Northern South Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Earlier this morning, the UN announced that the\Ndemocratic revolutionary army,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an organization based in various\Nparts of Asia, had been subjugated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The UN Chairman Brian Jackson\Nreported that "a young—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}—man suspected to be the ringleader, and that\Neveryone has been apprehended unhurt."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:04.93,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For what is to come, he answered,\N"We will look out for attacks from remaining forces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.52,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There even is a useful ability like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope there will be a quick,\Npeaceful resolution."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like there are other places\Nthat are gathering ability-wielders...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.12,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A city in Egypt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.71,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful of the One-Eyed Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-The One-Eyed Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What an embarrassing nickname...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't think I would be called that of all people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that? That image just now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I became able to learn what\Nthe plundered ability is without knowing it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, I plundered every\Nability of yet another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I took an ability to translate languages,\Nand an ability to be active without sleeping at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing. But, don't\Noverexert yourself too much, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... I have to finish off the next country\Nas soon as possible. Time is precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right... It may be rough, but I'm counting\Non you to be done before you lose your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An ability to make illnesses worse...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:52.87,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Northern Afghanistan Mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ability-wielders are all clumped up again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To make children do something like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One clump only has one glimmer...\NWhat does this mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the..? No images are popping up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a facility is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carriers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. They've been infected, but the ability\Nhasn't broken out yet, so they're carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I can't plunder an ability\Nbefore it breaks out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Exactly. The special abilities are truly a disease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, before particles are spread all over Earth again,\Nwe need to vaccinate every person in the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it's an illness, I can make it worse,\Nand have the ability break out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wouldn't that make plundering possible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, that went well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that new ability-wielders don't show up\Nfrom countries after I leave them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to plunder from all\Ncarriers as well from now on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:23.09,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern India
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot until you're out of ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.03,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Peru Republic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So there was someone with\Nan ability to heal...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad you got all better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry. Even if you were using your ability for good,\NI have to plunder it from you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This hand... If I put this hand on\Nmy right eye right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can regain my stature as\Nwielder of the time-leap ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I might be even able to save Kumagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it. I didn't plunder\Nabilities for something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow for acts that break\Nhuman reason any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn this world into\None with zero ability-wielders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is my only mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.47,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A city in Cuba
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:02.89,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming call - Shunsuke Otosaka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So are you my enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... Calm down...\NCalm down... I shouldn't kill anyone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.45,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Western Saudi Arabia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They have announced that they have captured\NMayor Muscle of their capital Hassan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to government insiders, an attack at the\Nmayor's mansion by the coup d'état army has started,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:08.04,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going here tomorrow... Once in a while, even if\NI have to force myself, I should sleep a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he is said to have\Nbeen captured at that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to government reports, this attack has\Nkilled at least 10 city legislators and injured 20 more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:16.18,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is necessary to rest one's body every so often...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Currently at the capital—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The government has announced this morning\Nthat the leader of the coup d'état,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mofsen bin Yagid, has agreed to unconditional surrender.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ongoing combat within the capital from last year were\Nby a syndicate that was comprised of primarily children,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.36,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.78,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but due to a skirmish yesterday instigated by a\Nmysterious individual, it seems they have suffered major damages.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.16,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With that, the coup d'état forces—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.91,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}—agreed that the syndicate led by\NMofsen will not be further prosecuted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:47.54,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... My memory is\Nstarting to muddle....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}... for other crimes, leaving the focus now to\Nhow the government will respond from hereon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:51.09,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I shouldn't sleep after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:54.26,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Southern Italy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world am I doing here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I in a battlefield..?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I made a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I would plunder every last\Nability in the world, and then return to her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her..?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who was she..?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she was someone\Nvery dear to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't remember who...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.28,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Russian Federation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... So someone with the "explosion"\Nability will show up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So you're that "Reaper"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you can die off together with our principles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the... Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That ability only gives people misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.60,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A city in the United Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.94,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A city in Sicily
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One-eyed..?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be... The Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm the Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:47.41,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manhattan, New York
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Reaper here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:10.68,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arizona
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is too tough for me... I don't want to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell came up with such a huge task,\Nand why did it end up that I had to do it..?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough, right? I'm tired\Nnow! Someone take over for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll just take over this entire Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm omnipotent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am God! I decide everything! That's what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I regretting kicking this thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I crying because of it..?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this...\NI still need to keep doing my best...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.83,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siberia, Irkutsk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:04.46,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Southern Cambodia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:23.15,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Turkey Northern Research Base
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't any of it hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the One-Eyed Grim Reaper!\NThere's no way we can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That surely defeated him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me! That was an RPG!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:04.57,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Southeastern Australia
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:14.28,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beijing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's close to here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got that Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't pick on the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pick on the weak? Do you know who the hell that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That guy has a huge bounty on his head!\NIf I nab him, I get a ton of cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, you shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I guess you'll have to\Nsee some pain as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you like! I will never stand aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ability of the very last ability-wielder...\Nwas the power of "courage", huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that is merely reckless valor...\NYou were about to die there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are a girl with more than enough courage.\NSo, you should be on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then, I'll go call for help!\NI'll make sure to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over, so I need to get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I accomplished everything...\Nso I need to get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get back...? To where..?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must have made a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can spend the rest\Nof my life fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finally awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all the hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You kept our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is not in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, you need to quietly rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how things roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you plundered thousands\N-tens of thousands - of abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...the stress caused by all that\Nto the brain must be staggering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a blessing that you can even talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...your lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A lover? Even though\NI don't recognize you at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts... a lot more than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make you sad just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because we were in the same class,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we lived our high school lives\Ntogether in the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And before you left,\Nyou promised me that we would be lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I can't remember anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those flash cards... I made those.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you held onto them until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did they come in handy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this... You made this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For me, this was something like a good-luck charm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was the one thing I couldn't part with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's so tattered, and half torn...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were able to come back\Nlike this because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make you sad again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm just happy. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it... but please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu Otosaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grave of the Kumagami family
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:23:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was a camcorder that I kept recording things\NI didn't want to record for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will record lots and lots of happy everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, let's leave behind lots\Nand lots of happy memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.23,0:23:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.06,0:23:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can Ayu be a part of that as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say right now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Everything is going to happen from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, let's fill our lives\Nonly with fun things.
